name: 'Totentanz' ~ iPhone case 5, 5s
description:
A front and back protection iPhone hard case for 5 and 5s, with Chrissy's 'Totentanz' artwork. This case is lightweight, durable and clips together for added protection against damaging phone and still maintains a slimline look.

The most fashionable way to protect your iPhone 5:
• Vivid high definition and long lasting printing
• Form fitting design with precise openings for keys and features

name: ' The Sinner & Saints ' ~ Mini Gift Card pack
description:
' The Sinner & Saint ' range consists of x6 of Chrissy's religious artworks. This is a great one if you like beautiful religious icons like 'The Sacred Heart', but also if you don't mind the occasional bad religious seed. This category is by far diverse in style and one of Chrissy's favourites. Each card comes with its own envelope, perfect for gifts.

Card specifics:

6 Gift Cards
6.35 X 6.35 cm
Each card comes with a brown craft envelope
Printed on Archival quality paper
Smooth Matte finish

name: 'Dia de Los Muertos' x2 Canvas Panels
description: 2 original pencil sketches on canvas panels by Chrissy M. Both panels are 12.7 X 17.8 cm. Sold as a couple they are signed and come with a pack of 10 stickers of other works by Chrissy.
